  "message": "chore(beads): rotate br_history issue snapshots \u2014 remove stale 2026-02-03 entries, add current 2026-02-16 state\n\nRemove 10 obsolete beads_rust issue history snapshots from 2026-02-03\nthat were superseded by the current issue database state, and add 10\nnew snapshots from 2026-02-16 reflecting the latest issue tracker\nstate after the reliability hardening and scheduler safety work.\n\nThe br_history directory maintains point-in-time JSONL snapshots of\nthe issue database for audit trail and rollback purposes. Old\nsnapshots are rotated out once the current state has been captured.\n\nCo-Authored-By: Claude <noreply@anthropic.com>",
